data.description: Stunning Attached Dwelling built in 2002 with a 0.03 Acre lot in Subdivision: Rocky Mountain Village 2nd Sub. Welcome to your new home at 4012 Plum Creek Drive in Loveland, Colorado! Nestled in the highly sought-after Centerra area, this charming attached dwelling offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. As you step into this well-maintained home, you'll be greeted by the warmth of pristine hardwood floors, complemented by elegant white cabinets and the inviting embrace of vaulted ceilings. With 2 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms spread across 1,512 square feet, you'll find spacious and comfortable living areas, perfect for your lifestyle.The finished basement offers versatility, with the potential to transform it into a third bedroom, and there's already a non-permitted bathroom in place, ready to accommodate your needs. Say goodbye to the hassle of snow removal thanks to the attached 2-car garage, adding a layer of convenience to your daily routine.Step outside into your private patio yard, complete with eco-friendly astroturf, providing a tranquil outdoor space where you can unwind and enjoy the Colorado sunshine.This Centerra gem is not only a beautiful home but also offers a prime location. With easy access to Highway US 34 and I-25, commuting is a breeze, making it perfect for professionals and families alike. You're also just moments away from fantastic shopping, dining, and entertainment options, ensuring that convenience is always at your doorstep.But it's not just about the immediate amenities. This community is surrounded by scenic trails, top-notch schools, picturesque parks, and a vibrant shopping and dining scene. Loveland's charm and recreational opportunities are yours to explore.Don't let this exceptional opportunity slip through your fingers. Make 4012 Plum Creek Drive your own and experience the Colorado lifestyle at its finest. Schedule a viewing today and make this exquisite property your dream home!
